thomasmcgee - if you really want a demonoid invite, you'll have to provide some contact info. But things are much better seeded here. Demonoid is safer, yes, but the pirate bay is MUCH faster.

Demonoid and TPB are just different no better or worse. I have not experienced demonoid being slow. I'd say in most cases there is a bigger variety here, but demonoid has a much better selection of mac specific software than TPB... as far as movies go Demonoid tends to have older ones too where as TPB does not. Sometimes I can only find certain things on one or the other and not both. 

As for an invite... I only invite people I know. I take inviting people to a private community very seriously.
